sysfs module example
====================

1. Compile the sysfs module:
$ make

2. Install the sysfs module:
$ sudo insmod my_sysfs.ko

3. Write a value to the sysfs variable:
$ echo "32" | sudo tee -a /sys/kernel/my_sysfs/my_variable

4. Print the value of the sysfs variable:
$ sudo cat /sys/kernel/my_sysfs/my_variable

5. Remove the sysfs module:
$ sudo rmmod my_sysfs.ko

